OL,7,FIt is the prosecution's case that
OL,8,FEthan was alone in a room with his
OL,9,Fgrandparents when he collapsed in
OL,10,Ftheir Garden City home.
OL,12,FThey say the mother Shannon was
OL,13,Fupstairs on the phone with a friend,
OL,14,Fcoming down when she was alerted that
OL,15,FEthan was unconscious.
OL,17,FNeither Kerry or Michael Ives accept
OL,18,Fresponsibility. Both say they were in
OL,19,Fthe room but offer no plausible reason
OL,20,Ffor the injuries he sustained,
OL,21,FCaroline Rees KC said.
