OL,7,FOn the night of 14th August 2021 Ethan
OL,8,Fcollapsed and an ambulance was called
OL,9,Fto the Garden City home where 6
OL,10,Fchildren and 3 adults were living.
OL,11,FEthan was unresponsive.
OL,13,FA 13 minute 999 call made by Kerry
OL,14,FIves was played in court.
OL,16,FShannon Ives looked down as the call
OL,17,Fwas played out, her father Michael
OL,18,Fleant forward and looked to the floor
OL,19,Fas Kerry Ives stared straight ahead.
