OL,8,Fbe heard saying "Ethan","Ethan" and
OL,9,F"come on lad".
OL,11,FPolice body cameras recorded the
OL,12,Finteraction between the couple and the
OL,13,Fpolice officers who attended the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FIn the footage Michael Ives tells
